                <h2>GRCC's Dual-Campus Structure: Two Locations, Two Courts</h2>
                <p>Grand Rapids Community College is Michigan's largest community college with over 11,000 students across multiple locations. The two main campuses create distinct legal jurisdictions that most attorneys don't understand.</p>

