                <p><strong>GRCC Main Campus Location:</strong> Downtown Grand Rapids (Main Campus and DeVos Campus)</p>
                <p><strong>Court Jurisdiction:</strong> 61st District Court, 180 Ottawa Ave NW, Grand Rapids, MI 49503</p>

                <p>If you're arrested in downtown Grand Rapids - whether on campus, at downtown bars, walking home from class, or anywhere in the city - your case will be prosecuted in 61st District Court.</p>

