                </ul>

                <p>The 61st District Court is a high-volume urban court serving Michigan's second-largest city. Prosecutors handle thousands of cases, and the court moves quickly. Having local counsel who appears regularly in this court is essential.</p>

                <h3>Holland Lakeshore Campus - 58th District Court</h3>
