                    <li>The Michigan Board of Nursing reviews criminal history for licensure - drug convictions, theft, assault, and crimes of dishonesty often result in license denial</li>
                    <li>Even if GRCC allows you to continue in the program, you may be unable to obtain state licensure to practice as a nurse</li>
                </ul>

